Version 1.1.2 (2012-03-29)

    * Added --this option functioning as alias for this host.
    
Version 1.1.0 (2012-03-28)

    * Added -F (--close) option for closing all logon events matching
      the filter preferences.
      
    * Session mode (-S) is now supported on Linux.
    
    * Added manual page and improving documentation. Applying GPL 3 to
      the source code.
      
    * Support for extracting username and domain from Kerberos 5
      tickets.
      
    * Ported code to Mac OS X.

Version 1.0.0 (2011-11-23)

    * Initial release
    
